description:
This is a 9 minute workout called 'Quick Morning Stretching Routine For Flexibility, Mobility, And Stiffness!' from the channel Tone and Tighten.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Improve flexibility and mobility by following along with this complete total-body routine first thing every morning.
